    <item>
      <title>乌克兰电网暂停债券支付以等待债务改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ukraine-s-power-grid-halts-bond-payments-awaiting-debt-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰电网运营商 NPC Ukrenergo 暂停其 2028 年到期的美元计价票据的服务，直至与债券持有人达成重组协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ukraine-s-power-grid-halts-bond-payments-awaiting-debt-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 12:14:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选 欧元兑美元汇率创 2016 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/euro-parity-back-in-play-as-trump-win-spurs-rates-divergence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统竞选中的胜利增加了欧洲大幅降息的可能性，推动欧元与美元汇率趋于平价，货币交易员开始看空欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/euro-parity-back-in-play-as-trump-win-spurs-rates-divergence</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 10:53:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金将里拉视为特朗普货币混乱的避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/hedge-funds-turn-to-lira-as-haven-from-trump-currency-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫的前景导致全球其他货币汇率下跌，土耳其里拉成为周三唯一兑美元上涨的新兴市场货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/hedge-funds-turn-to-lira-as-haven-from-trump-currency-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 10:21:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农业信贷银行债务交易员表现优异，保险表现落后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/credit-agricole-beats-estimates-as-debt-traders-outperform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 公布第三季度利润高于预期，因为其债务交易商的表现优于竞争对手，而分析师则关注令人失望的保险和消费金融收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/credit-agricole-beats-estimates-as-debt-traders-outperform</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税风险冲击欧元、德国汽车股；可再生能源下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/european-stock-futures-drop-over-tariff-worries-as-trump-leads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利加剧了人们对全面关税的担忧，欧元创下了四年多以来的最大单日跌幅，而汽车制造商等对美国收入依赖较大的行业表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/european-stock-futures-drop-over-tariff-worries-as-trump-leads</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:44:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
